  "timeline-content/intro.html": "<div class=\"context-card context-card-sky\">\n    <img src=\"../assets/rw_university_1902.jpg\" alt=\"Roger Williams University 1902\" class=\"thumbnail-img-inline\">\n    <p>As emancipation reshaped the South, education became a powerful symbol of self-determination.</p>\n    <p>Newly freed people joined with established Black Nashvillians to build and sustain schools that embodied collective resilience.</p>\n    <p>These efforts transformed Nashville into a regional hub of Black intellectual and spiritual life, creating institutions that would shape the future of African American education throughout the South.</p>\n    <div class=\"cb\"></div>\n</div>",
